node.text: A short film made by my boy @yungjalapeneaux along with @alexanderkreig @mattsbelldp  he spent an incredible amount of time on this and it came out a masterpiece. Please tag and share it to every human you know, even ur cat. There is also a link in my bio to watch it on youtube.
